                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The infiltrators draw or reload concealed hand crossbows and launch a hail of bolts in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 60 feet that deals @Damage[5d6[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:23|basic] save). When the unit is reduced to 2 segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
